net.sf.mmm.util.collection.base

Class CustomHashKey<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.collection.base.AbstractHashKey<T>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.collection.base.CustomHashKey<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the generic type of the delegate-object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CustomHashKey<T>
extends AbstractHashKey<T>
    This is a simple wrapper in order to use an object as hash key but with ability to customize equals and hashCode.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
